# Tips

- Netlify link if a project is already in the website
    
- netlify dev 
    
- No need to commit to keep doing netlify build
    

  

# Netlify dev keeps getting stuck in port 3000

# Solution : Add this to vite.config.ts
```

 server:{

    host:true,

    port:3000

  }
```
